## **What This App Does for Chronic Illness Patients**

### **The Problem:**
People with chronic illness track symptoms, foods, supplements, sleep, etc. but can't see the 
patterns. They're drowning in data without insights.

### **The Solution - 3 Powerful Categories:**

#### **1. TRIGGERS TO AVOID** 
• **Individual foods**: "Eggs trigger your swelling 100% of the time"
• **Grouped triggers**: Shows one food causing multiple symptoms
• **Actionable**: Clear elimination targets

#### **2. THINGS THAT HELP**
• **Supplements that work**: "Melatonin 3mg reduces 4 symptoms: headache, joint pain, swelling, 
digestive issues"
• **Grouped benefits**: Shows multi-symptom helpers
• **Actionable**: Clear intervention targets

#### **3. TRENDS (Most Powerful)**
• **Chemical property patterns**: "High salicylate foods trigger swelling" 
• **Groups foods by compounds**: oxalate, lectin, histamine, nightshade, FODMAP, salicylate
• **Reveals hidden sensitivities**: Not just "avoid broccoli" but "avoid high salicylate foods"
• **Actionable**: Whole food category elimination

## **The Power:**
Instead of "I feel bad and don't know why," patients get:
• **Clear triggers to eliminate**
• **Proven helpers to continue** 
• **Hidden chemical patterns** they never would have discovered

This transforms chronic illness management from guesswork to data-driven precision medicine.

That's the goal - and we're very close to delivering it robustly.

